snippet.title: Funny Thing About Love - Clip (Exclusive) [Ultimate Film Trailers]
snippet.description:
Funny Thing About Love (PG)
In Theatres December 3rd, 2021 |© 2021 Gravitas Ventures

Samantha Banks is on top of the world, a successful business, and a handsome fiancé. But over one crazy Thanksgiving Holiday with her scheming family, her whole world is thrown into a tailspin when they invite her ex-boyfriend, "the one that got away".

Director: Adam White
Writers: Adam White
Actors: Jon Heder, Summer Bellessa, Barry Corbin, Pat Finn, Jason Gray, Brooke White, Kevan Moezzi
Genre: Romance, Comedy
Run Time: 1 hour 36 minutes
